-- Cimatron Surges Most in 5 Months in Israel on Cash Distribution
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-04-18T12:55:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-18/cimatron-surges-most-in-5-months-in-israel-on-cash-distribution.html
Cimatron Ltd. (CIMT)  soared the most in
almost five months after the provider of software products for
manufacturing industries said it received court approval for a
$10 million cash distribution to shareholders.  The  shares climbed  13 percent, the most on an intraday
basis since Nov. 29, to 15.55 shekels at 1:02 p.m. in  Tel Aviv .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
